#. module: hm_sale_crm
#: model:mail.template,body_html:hm_sale_crm.mail_template_interview_tracking_mail_client_time_to_plan
msgid ""
"<p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: "
"rgb(156, 156, 148); font-style: initial; font-variant-ligatures: initial; "
"font-variant-caps: initial; font-weight: initial; text-align: "
"inherit;\">***Cet e-mail a été transmis aux adresses suivantes:</span><span "
"style=\"text-align: inherit;\"><font "
"color=\"#9c9c94\">&nbsp;${object.hm_partner.email or '''-'''} "
"-&nbsp;</font><font "
"color=\"#9c9c94\">${object.dest_address_id.email or '''-'''} "
"-&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"text-align: inherit;\"><font "
"color=\"#9c9c94\">"
"</font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 156, 148); text-align: "
"inherit; font-style: initial; font-variant-ligatures: initial; font-variant-"
"caps: initial; font-weight: initial;\">&nbsp;***</span></p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-"
"align: inherit;\"><font color=\"#9c9c94\"><br></font></span><span "
"style=\"font-style: initial; font-variant-ligatures: initial; font-variant-"
"caps: initial; font-weight: initial; text-align: inherit;\">Cher "
"client,</span><br></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-"
"family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-"
"serif;\">Selon notre système de suivi il est temps d'organiser le prochain "
"<b style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><u>entretien </u></b>de votre installation "
"technique.</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-"
"family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-"
"serif;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-"
"family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-"
"serif;\"><u>Concerne l'installation située à l'adresse suivante:</u></p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-"
"weight:bolder;\">${object.dest_address_id.contact_address}</b></p><p"
" style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\">Sauf avis contraire, "
"l'intervention sera facturée au client suivant:</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 "
"1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, "
"Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\">${object.hm_partner.name}</p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\">Pourriez-vous nous "
"transmettre une ou plusieurs dates qui vous conviendraient durant le mois à "
"venir afin d'organiser cela au mieux? Ceci par simple réponse à ce mail. Si "
"vous avez des demandes particulières, n'hésitez pas à nous en faire "
"part.</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-"
"family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-"
"serif;\"><br>Nous sommes à votre disposition pour toute question.</p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p "
"style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida "
"Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\">L'équipe Heat "
"Me</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida"
" Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\">+32 (0)2 486 76 "
"76</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0 1rem 0;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida"
" Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p>"
msgstr ""

